            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3EEssential%20to%20the%20most%20basic%20faith%20in%20God%20is%20the%20belief%20that%20He%20is%20coming.%20From%20the%20time%20of%20Enoch%2C%20who%20Genesis%205%3A22%20declares%20lived%20%22in%20close%20fellowship%20with%20God%2C%22%20faithful%20believers%20have%20understood%20that%20He%20is%20coming%20to%20judge%20everyone%20(Jude%2014-15).%20The%20thief%20on%20the%20cross%20was%20saved%20just%20by%20saying%2C%20%22Jesus%2C%20remember%20me%20when%20you%20come%20into%20your%20Kingdom%22%20(Luke%2023%3A42).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20Lord%20will%20return%20suddenly%20and%20swiftly%20to%20judge%20the%20ungodly.%20Just%20as%20Gideon%20descended%20with%20a%20trumpet%20blast%20in%20the%20night%20in%20sudden%20judgment%20upon%20Midian%20(Judges%207%3A19)%2C%20Jesus%20will%20suddenly%20return%20with%20His%20saints%20to%20judge%20the%20world.%20If%20you%20are%20%22faint%2C%20yet%20pursuing%22%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E(8%3A4%20KJV)%2C%20keep%20up%20the%20fight.%20Your%20blessed%20hope%20as%20a%20believer%20is%20that%20the%20Lord%20will%20return%20not%20only%20to%20deliver%20you%20from%20this%20world%20but%20also%20to%20punish%20His%20enemies%20who%20have%20afflicted%20you.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EPaul%20reminded%20the%20Philippian%20believers%20that%20%22we%20are%20citizens%20of%20heaven%2C%20where%20the%20Lord%20Jesus%20Christ%20lives.%20And%20we%20are%20eagerly%20waiting%20for%20him%20to%20return%20as%20our%20Savior%20(Philippians%203%3A20).%20.%20.%20.%20Remember%2C%20the%20Lord%20is%20coming%20soon%22%20(4%3A5).%20One%20day%20the%20Lord%20will%20descend%20from%20heaven%2C%20and%20our%20battle%20will%20be%20eternally%20over!%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
        {
            "id": "ot-passage",
